/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/meta-inbox/meta-exploration-002.md:16:For Tao-filter steps, demand an estimate-level lever on the exact live obstruction. If a candidate cannot name the quantity it shrinks, treat it as dead even if it is genuinely NS-specific in some broader sense.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/selector.md:14:Chain 01 stays first because it has the best expected value. It tests the cleanest remaining algebraic reserve path, front-loads the Tao screen, and still produces a sharp obstruction memo if every natural reformulation collapses back to the same estimate-level bottleneck.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/selector.md:16:Chain 02 stays second because it is the strongest remaining genuinely geometric branch and has a high-quality failure mode. Its structure is disciplined: it separates Beltrami alignment, direction coherence, and tube persistence, then forces an early confrontation with the full stretching term rather than allowing descriptive vortex language to substitute for control.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:7:But the chain is still too optimistic and too loose. It mostly formalizes a future-work note that already existed in the prior mission rather than introducing a new discriminating lemma, model calculation, or early Tao-compatible kill test. The main risk is that it spends budget renorming a harmonic function whose size is still dictated by the same remote shell energy `E_0`.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:41:This is also where the chain quietly assumes that a harmonic estimate can be "non-De-Giorgi" while still proving something Tao-relevant. That is not convincing. If the gain uses only elliptic regularity of a harmonic tail, it is almost certainly available in averaged NS too.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:43:## Step 4 - Apply the Tao filter and close the chain
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:45:The Tao filter is placed too late. That is a structural mistake.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:47:Everything in Step 2 is generic elliptic/harmonic analysis: local `H^1`, `BMO`, Campanato, Carleson, mean-value, interior gradient, Harnack-type decay. Tao's averaged model is designed to survive exactly this level of analysis. If a candidate route does not use an NS-specific identity before the norm-testing phase, it should be presumed guilty immediately, not checked at the end.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:49:The comparison criterion is also too weak. "Does the argument use exact NS pressure structure or only generic elliptic harmonicity?" is the right question, but the chain gives no mechanism for answering it. A real filter would force the route to identify the specific NS-only ingredient up front, for example some exploitable fact about `\partial_i \partial_j p = R_i R_j(u_i u_j)` that is not preserved by Tao's averaging. If the route cannot name that ingredient by the end of Step 1, it is probably dead already.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-001/attacks/chain-01.md:65:But as a planning object it is still too soft. It needs an earlier Tao filter, an explicit shell-source countermodel, and a quantitative definition of success tied to the bad coefficient `C_far`, not just "stronger than `O(E_0)`." Without those upgrades, the most likely outcome is a polished restatement of why harmonicity gives smoothness but not the kind of NS-specific smallness the problem actually needs.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/planner-chains/chain-04.md:5:The exact tensor identities of NS may carry information that scalar norm estimates erase. The key objects are the strain tensor `S`, the pressure Hessian `nabla^2 p`, and the stretching identity `omega . nabla u = S omega`. This chain tests whether eigenframe dynamics, sign structure, or tensor-level depletion yields a usable rigidity or conditional regularity lever that Tao's averaged operator would not preserve.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/planner-chains/chain-04.md:20:### Step 1 - Compile the exact tensor identities and front-load the Tao screen
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/building_models/current_hunts/big-thinkers/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-002/planner-chains/chain-04.md:23:- Action: assemble the pointwise and transport identities linking `S`, `nabla^2 p`, and `omega`, and separate formulas that are exact NS structure from formulas that are only Calderon-Zygmund repackaging.
